<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        .main-container{
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            width: 620px;
            margin: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .username{
            font-size: 24px;
            font-family: Arial,serif;
            color: #666;
        }

        .content{
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-family: Arial,serif;
        }

        .metawarn{
            font-size: 12px;
            font-family: Arial,serif;
            text-align: justify;
            text-justify: inter-word;
            background-color : #FFF3CF;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #846315;
        }

        body{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .go-button{
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px;
            border: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
    <body>
        <div class="main-container">
            <div class="username">Hello <%=firstName%> !</div>
            <p class="content">
                Your request to join the UCSC Results Center has being accepted by an administrator. Now you can access the system view results and analysis.
            </p>
            <a href="https://ucscresults.herokuapp.com" target="_blank">
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <button class="go-button">Visit UCSC Results Center</button>
                </div>
            </a>
            <p class="metawarn">UCSC Results Center (https://ucscresults.herokuapp.com) is neither affiliated with the Examination Branch of University of Colombo School of Computing nor the University of Colombo School of Computing itself. The formulas and methodologies used by this system may not be the same the formulas and methodologies used to calculate you GPA, Rank and your class by the Examination Department of University of Colombo School of Computing. Therefore, the data and the methodologies used by this system can be wrong, and the administrator or any attached partners of the system is not responsible for any kind of result/loss occurred by using the information generated by this system.<p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>